{
  "stem": "23645.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Skarzysko, there was an ammunitions factory, by the name of HASAG.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have some details on, on that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was an organization-- a factory from Germany that just came over and established themself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were doing munitions and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- there was a call out to, to the Jewish people, first, to come and work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they would get paid and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So some of them did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But then afterwards, it was obligatory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Any abled men or women, if you didn't come voluntarily, they would just find you on the street and put you to work there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did your father go to work?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to give it up when-- we had to-- so-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had to close the doors pretty well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went, had a work permit, and went to work in the munitions factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so did my brothers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my sister also had a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was tending cows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A lot of the young girls were rounded up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were looking after this farm that belonged to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there were-- and, as a matter of fact, I remember my mother worrying about her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know where they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was sort of like an hour and a half walking, where this farm was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She cooked up some chicken soup and some chicken and some lokshen and some-- a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a part of a bit of a cholent.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there I was, taking this to my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I was still able to walk free and brought her this food.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
